---
import WhatsAppButton from '../../WhatsAppButton.astro'
import { buildWhatsAppHref } from '../../../data/site'

const waHref = buildWhatsAppHref()
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden bg-petrol-50 py-24 md:py-32'>
  <!-- Subtle dot grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,60,74,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;'>
  </div>

  <!-- Large faded watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none overflow-hidden'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive; font-size: clamp(12rem, 26vw, 22rem); color: rgba(249,115,22,0.05); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'>
    SOLUCIÓN
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8'>
    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-start'>

      <!-- ── LEFT: Headline block ─────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='lg:sticky lg:top-28'>
        <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-8'>
          <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-orange-500' aria-hidden='true'></span>
          <h2 class='label-section text-orange-500'>
            Contratar un consultor SEO
          </h2>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'
          class='leading-[0.9] tracking-tight'>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3.5rem)] text-petrol-700 mb-1'>
            Pero se puede
          </span>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(3.2rem,7.5vw,5.5rem)] text-petrol-900'>
            solucionar<span class='text-orange-400'>.</span>
          </span>
        </p>

        <div data-animate class='mt-6 flex items-center gap-0'>
          <div class='h-[3px] w-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/40 to-transparent'></div>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='mt-6 max-w-[40ch] text-base md:text-lg text-petrol-700 leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
          En cuanto me envíes ese WhatsApp, analizo tu web gratis en menos de 24 horas y te digo exactamente <strong class='text-petrol-900 font-semibold'>qué hay que hacer para que tus clientes te encuentren en Google.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── RIGHT: 4-step process ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='flex flex-col'>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-petrol-100'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='label-micro text-orange-400 leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-orange-400/40 tabular-nums'
              style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'>
              01
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-petrol-900 mb-3'>
              Pulsa aquí
            </p>
            <WhatsAppButton
              text='Analiza mi web'
              href={waHref}
              class='text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2.5 shadow-sm shadow-sky-500/20'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-petrol-100'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='label-micro text-orange-400 leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-orange-400/40 tabular-nums'
              style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'>
              02
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-petrol-900 mb-3'>
              Dime este mensaje
            </p>
            <div class='bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200/70 rounded-xl rounded-tl-sm px-4 py-3'>
              <p class='text-sm text-orange-700 italic leading-relaxed'>
                "Salva, mi página web es invisible en Barcelona."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-petrol-100'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='label-micro text-orange-400 leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-orange-400/40 tabular-nums'
              style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'>
              03
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-petrol-900 mb-2'>
              Esta es mi página web
            </p>
            <p class='text-sm text-petrol-700 leading-relaxed'>
              Comparte la URL de tu negocio. Nada más.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 pt-10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='label-micro text-orange-400 leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-orange-400/40 tabular-nums'
              style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'>
              04
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class='flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2'>
              <p class='text-base font-bold text-petrol-900'>
                En menos de
              </p>
              <span
                style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'
                class='text-2xl leading-none text-orange-400'>
                24h
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class='text-sm text-petrol-700 leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
              Me pongo en contacto contigo, te explico por qué tu web no
              posiciona y qué voy a hacer para que aparezca en primera
              página de Google.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
